body.p:
In the Classpath tab you can perform the following actions:

 New - opens a dialog that allows
          you to add a resource in the Classpath tab;

 Edit - opens a dialog
          that allows you to edit a resource in the Classpath tab;

 Delete - deletes the
          currently selected resource;

 Move Up - moves the
          selection to the previous resource;

 Move Down - moves
          the selection to the following resource.
